name: Sand Castle
description: It is a child's play to make something this sturdy.

name: Earthworks
description: One hole is better than no hole.

name: Summoning Circle
description: I summon thee, the Sleeping One.

name: False Floor
description: I'm sure this is the right way...

name: Caratos
description: Look away and he'll eat your soul!

name: Golden Rabbit
description: I saw a golden rabbit one day. It ran really fast. Like REALLY fast.

name: Dark-one Spy
description: You see him now. Oh, you missed him.

name: Earth Elemental
description: It blends in to the hillside. It punches you in the face.

name: Iron Spirit
description: Iron claws will tear you apart

name: Sand Ghost
description: Towering over a thousand foot, it looks down and laughs at you.

name: Armor of Healing
description: Clumsy and clanging. Still feels good.

name: Immovable Shelter
description: In the wind, it's nice to remain still.

name: Tooth and Nail
description: Sometimes you need to keep your grip to reality with tooth and nail.
